    ConnectionProcessor is a Runnable that is executed on a background thread to submit session & event data to a Count.wigzo.ly server. NOTE: This class is only public to facilitate unit testing, because of this bug in dexmaker: https://code.google.com/p/dexmaker/issues/detail?id=34
